# SwayWM global configuration. For detailed information type "man sway"
# Author: Oscar Carballal Prego <oscar.carballal@protonmail.com>

###############################################################################
# TODO:
#   + Sway:
#      - Autoassign workspaces to certain applications
#      - Unlock keychain after login
